    "detailed_description": "Logical circuit is a beautiful and colorful puzzles game, where it will make you think about how to form several paths so that each of the balls reach the end where appropriate.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe game has 60 challenges with which you can think and have fun, the difficulty is increasing based on the progress of the challenges.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe objective of the game is to make metal balls fall on the bottom tray, in each tray a certain amount of balls must enter, you can define the path of the balls based on the pieces that you place on the board.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMove the pieces to create a path and get the metal marbles to reach the base of the board, you must make each of the bases fall a corresponding number of marbles.",
